Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.72,0:00:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 这电影肯定不是根据真实故事改编的\NOk, in no way is this movie based on a true story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这绝对会在未来发生\NIt's a future  true story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,僵尸启示录一定会变成现实的\NA zombie apocalypse is going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.43,0:00:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,要不你以为我为啥像现在这样生活呢?\NI mean, why do you think I live the way I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 没志向 缺乏自尊心 - 不讲信用\NMm, lack of ambition, no self-respect. Credit score in the ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,错 是因为僵尸!\NNo, guys. Zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.94,0:00:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,研究表明我们之中只有一人幸免于难\NI mean, studies show only one of us would survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是...这个人是谁呢?\NThe question is... Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.29,0:00:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这取决于生存技巧 你们懂不?\NDepends on survival strategy, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就好比我们是反抗他们\NIt's like are we talking strength to fight them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,还是混入其中?\NOr ability to blend in and live amongst them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,混入其中?我们现在"混入其中"了么?\NAmongst? Are we doing "amongst" now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.35,0:00:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯哪  - 咱认真点行不?这可是生死攸关\NMm-hmm. Can we focus up here? Okay? This is life and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 要说能和僵尸混到一块的，那肯定是戴夫\NAll right. If we're gonna do ability to blend in, I say Dave.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,反正他现在基本也就一僵尸了 -什么?!\NHe's basically a zombie anyway. What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.09,0:00:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 哥们 我知道你的日程\NYeah, I've seen your daily routine, bro--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.09,0:00:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,早上7点起床 洗澡 吃万年不变的纤维麦片\NWake up at 7:00, shower, eat the same fiber-based cereal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那绝对是中老年妇女的青睐\NThat is clearly geared towards menopausal women.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.53,0:00:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,人家吃的"嘎嘣脆"是适合所有年龄段的啊\N"her choice crunch" is for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,额  -而且和僵尸一样 你没有任何梦想\NEee. And like a zombie, you don't really have any hopes or dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我有梦想!  -真的?\NI have dreams! Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我还在为我的餐馆梦想而奋斗  -哦 是么\NLook, I am still working on opening my own restaurant. Oh, yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.77,0:00:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,貌似六年前你也提过这么档子事\NYou were just mentioning that, like, six years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.93,0:00:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 但是我\NYeah, but I de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚做了美味的牛排三明治啊\NThese delicious steak sandwiches for us tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.91,0:00:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然马科斯的烤箱最高只能烧到60度\NDespite the fact that Max's oven only goes up to 150.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.58,0:01:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 如果僵尸入侵 我敢说最先挂的\NWell, I could tell you who would die first in a zombie attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是马科斯\NI mean, it's obviously Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我吐两次来表明\NI did that double spit take to illustrate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.86,0:01:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚刚的话听起来有多蠢\NHow insane you sound right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.68,0:01:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 布拉德 可是简会先死  -我?\NI'm sorry, Brad, but Jane would die first. Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.10,0:01:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  -你身材走样 没有实才\NOh, yeah. You are out of shape, you have no marketable talents,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你没有任何生存技能\NAnd you have no survival skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,相对的 虽然你有你热爱的东西\NCounterpoint--there are things in this world that you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.70,0:01:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但你终究会被他们拖累 我的冷酷的内心\NThat slows people down. My cold, black heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.97,0:01:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,以及避免我和其他人或物\NAnd living without attachments
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.47,0:01:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,产生纠葛 这才是我的优势所在啊\NTo anyone or anything--it's my greatest asset right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.89,0:01:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样 哥们 她真的很好战\NDon't do this, dude. She is seriously competitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.14,0:01:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,59个热狗\Nwith that 59th hot dog,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,小林是目前最具竞争力的大胃王\NKobayashi is now the best competitive eater in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,给我准备60个热狗和一个煮蛋定时器\NI need 60 hot dogs and an egg timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.95,0:01:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们开始僵尸之战吧 疯狂的热狗女\NLet the zombie Olympics begin, crazy hot dog lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管放马过来\NBring it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,各就位 预备 跑!\NOn your mark, get set, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.06,0:01:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,加油啊 亲爱的 超过他\NMake it work, baby. Get him, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,难道我真的像僵尸?\NSo I'm really a zombie?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 振作点啊\NHey, you could stand to shake things up a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道肉类推销员不是什么理想的工作\NI know that selling meat isn't a dream job,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但收入很可观啊 而且它还和餐馆业沾边\NBut I make good money, it's restaurant-adjacent,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我才刚刚开始喜欢这种小生活\NAnd I just got comfortable taking deuces there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.06,0:01:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,往好的方面想想\NWell, you know, on the bright side,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:01:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,僵尸现在很火啊\NZombies are super in right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.98,0:02:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那我宁愿做个吸血鬼\NI'd rather be a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哥们 我们都更乐意做吸血鬼\Nwe'd all rather be vampires, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.51,0:02:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,哦!  -啊!\N(Jane) ohh! (Max) aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,搞定! 此时马科斯的脸\NCrushed it! Right now Max's face
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,正被僵尸们啃食呐  -这一局说明不了什么\NIs being eaten off by zombies. This is not over between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那就放马过来啊\NBring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.51,0:02:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你现在是我的了 不是么?\NOkay, I own you, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.16,0:02:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在你大脑中 而且我拥有3间卧室\NI am in your head, and I got a 3-bedroom condo in there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,1个大理石台 1个披萨烤箱\NWith a marble island and a pizza oven
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一台装满好酒的冰箱!\NAnd a wine fridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我们知道了\NOkay, we got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.33,0:02:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 不过亲爱的你知道那是我理想中的\NOkay, but you do know that that's my dream kitchen,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,厨房吧?  -你们...你们就这么走么?\NRight, babe? You guys... You guys just go, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我就要飙起来了\NI'm about to hit my runner's high.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,咱今晚上就出去 我们来大干一场!\NWe're going out tonight. We're gonna do it big!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.14,0:02:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HB76C22&}幸福终点站\N第一季  第07集\N==深影字幕组==
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我洗衣日的着装实在不想让人看见\NMy laundry day outfit is not meant for public eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 反正这只是个自助洗衣店\NIt's all right. It's a laundromat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,来这的都是怪胎\NEveryone here's a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,恩...不是说你\NWell... Not... You.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我得换点零钱去\NOh, you know what? I gotta get some quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,穿的不错啊\NNice outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:03:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,哈 你也是 你经常来?\NHa. You, too. So you come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,衣服脏的时候才来\NOnly when mylothes are dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 这么一说咱俩还真有共同点\NOh, so we have that in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.59,0:03:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我是托比\NI'm Toby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,彭妮\NPenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这烘干机烘件衣服要N久\NYou know, these dryers take forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,去隔壁喝杯咖啡..怎么样?  -嗯...\NYou... Wanna go next door, get a cup of coffee? Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊\NSure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.85,0:03:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NYeah. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.76,0:03:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那份脑子你传真过去没?\NDid you fax the brains?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你看见第三区的脑子没?\NDid you see the third quarter brains?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,上后腰脊肉10美元一磅\NTop sirloin's $10 a poun
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,速冻的 绝对保证营养\NIt's flash-frozen to retain all the nutrients.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢您致电本公司 祝您心情愉快\NThank you for calling trans corps. Have a great day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我花尽了心思打扮\NI spend so much time trying to look good,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,结果我穿的邋里邋遢的时候\NAnd then I wear my grungiest outfit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然有帅哥看上我了\NAnd a cute guy is into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我以后应该多多光顾自助洗衣店\NI should hang out at laundromats more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.51,0:03:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然要洗一大堆的内衣裤\NYes, I'll have to put up with a lot of abandoned underpants,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但是有偶尔出现的帅哥啊\NBut every on in a while, cute guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,款爷在这呢 这不比那些免费的内衣好的多么\NRockefeller over here-- too good for free underpants.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真是等不及让你们见见托比了\NI cannot wait for you guys to meet Toby!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 我们简直是志趣相投\NOh, my god. We are into all the same things--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,都喜欢家庭购物网 还有网上的宠物宝宝\NThe home shopping network, baby animals on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他甚至很欣赏我的刺绣\NHe even thinks it's cool that I needlepoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 你是不是在跟我奶奶约会\NI gotta tell you, it sounds like you're dating my grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 简的短信\NOh, I just got a text from Jane.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她要继续在我脑子里施工?\NShe's building an addition on the condo she has in my brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不带这样的 现在是休战期\NNot okay. Not during a recession.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,托比来了 他咋还穿成那样?\NToby's here. Why is he still dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 神啊 你知道他是什么人了吧?\NOh, my god. You know what he is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.21,0:04:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他是一嬉皮士 -不可能\NHe's a hipster. Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,紧身牛仔裤 四季带围巾\NThe skinny jeans, the scarf no matter the season.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,彭妮 这家伙绝对一嬉皮士\NThis guy's a hipster, penny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢的那些东西 他一概藐视  -你胡扯\NAll those things you like-- he likes them ironically. You don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我可没有 我站在这就能感受到他的气息\NYes, I do. I can smell him from here, and he smells like
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他绝对从跳蚤市场来  -你闭嘴\NA flea market. Watch your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 你收拾好没?\NOh, hey. You ready to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,听说有个很赞的混音作品的地下交换会\NJust heard about this awesome underground mix-tape swap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,马科斯说的对\NMax was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 那个用来锁自行车的东西\NHey, uh, that bike lock out there--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的皮带吧?  -是啊 帅吧?\NIs that also your belt? Oh, I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.71,0:04:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,超帅\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯...怎么今天这么打扮?\NSo... What's with the getup?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 这个么...\NOh, um... Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这个...\NIt's, uh... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是彭妮的洗衣日\NIt's penny's laundry day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定很喜欢洗衣服\NYou must love doing laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.69,0:05:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我有超强的吸灰能力 浑身上下都是\NI really attract stains, you know? All over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,咱走吧  -行 再见\NLet's head out. All right. See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你  -我们真的很开心\NNice to meet you. The pleasure is ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,别紧张哦\NTake it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你们说的对\NYou guys were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我就一僵尸\NI'm a zombie--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,工作时是 和阿莱克斯一起时也是\Nin my job, with Alex.
