Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你想吃墨西哥菜 而她想吃日本菜\NAnd you want Mexican. She wants Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你怎么做? - 那我们就吃日本菜\NWhat do you do? - we get Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,完全正确 没有选择的余地\NExactly. There's no way to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是我为什么给你们带来\NThat's why I give you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,泛大陆烧烤\NPangaea grill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,来自 125 个民族的 900 道菜\N900 dishes from 125 ethnic cuisines
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,都在菜单上了 宝贝\NAll on one menu, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 是啊 看上去有很多\NOh. Right. seems like a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你在复印店花了 17000 美元弄的么?\NDid you spend $17,000 at the copy store?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.12,0:11:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这需要启动资金\NAnd I know this is gonna take capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我为啥明天\NThat's why tomorrow I am meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要去见一个饭店投资人\NWith a restaurant investor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那是重点 伙计们! 我们来庆祝一下!\NThis is it, guys! Let's celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.09,0:11:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,泛大陆烧烤 香槟就来了\NPangaea grill. Champ comin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事 布拉德?\NWhat the hell, Brad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你和 戴夫 谈过了\NI thought you talked to Dave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我得说\NI gotta say,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,每一次我决定追逐这个梦想\NEver since I decided to pursue this dream again,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我都很兴奋，我以前的世界都是一团漆黑\NI'm so happy. I mean, I went to a dark place, man--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.18,0:11:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但感觉就是黎明前的黑暗\NLike applying-to-grad-school dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 你想说些什么?\NI'm sorry. What did you wanna talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.53,0:11:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,呃... Hillary clinton（克林顿总统的夫人）\NUh... Hillary clinton--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我给她投票了 我还没给任何说呢\NI voted for her. I never told anybody that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.59,0:11:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,跟人说一说真的很爽\NFeels really good to get it off my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,中途有点小故障\NThere was a glitch in the brave-length.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 总得有人要和他谈谈\N- Okay, someone needs to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.78,0:11:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，不然他就要在芝加哥卖土著民鲸鱼墨西哥卷\NYes, before he starts feeding chicago inuit blubber tacos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 肯定不能是我\NWell, it can't be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这一年我几乎都毁了他的私人生活\NI've already crushed his entire personal life this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.62,0:12:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不能在毁掉他的事业\NI cannot blow up his professional life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在生活还没支点呢\NI'm not at a point right now in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我又去哪找呢 - 好了 呃 必须有人\N- Where I can be taken seriously. - Okay, well, somebody has got
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 和他谈谈 这是必须的 - 戴夫!嘿!\N- To talk to him. This is absolutely - Dave! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿莱 帮我一下? - 恩 当然\N- Al, can yohelp me? - Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们 我真的得谢谢你们的支持\NGuys, I wanna thank you for your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道 没有你们的信任\NYou know, I couldn't do this without ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.77,0:12:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我是做不到的 套用缅甸的俗话说\NThank you for believing in me, or as they say in burmese...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,叽里大呱啦\NKyeizu tin ba de.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 香槟献给我真诚的朋友\NAll right. Champagne for my real friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,伤害留给我虚伪的朋友\NReal pain for my sham friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,为了 泛大陆\NTo Pangaea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,为了泛大陆  泛大陆\NTo Pangaea. Pangaea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,泛大陆\NPangaea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 冒泡了 - 泛大陆\N- bubble. - Pangaea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你在我脑中弄的公寓怎么样了 哈?\NHow's the condo you're building in my brain now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么? 干得太快导致经济崩溃了吗?\NWhat's that? You built it too quick and the economy collapsed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,而现在你不得不上街去以出卖体力为生\NAnd now you're out on the street doing hand stuff for food,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 哦!怎么又是平局?\NAnd--ohh! How do we tie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,又是 2 比 2?\N2-2 again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 好了 在这次的僵尸比赛中\NOkay, okay. There is one category left
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一项没有比 那就是比谁更无情\NIn this zombie-athalon-- ruthlessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但我还没想到怎么做\NBut I haven't figured out how to measure that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.43,0:12:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 打劫婴儿\NOh. Mug a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不是，不过方向是对的\NNo. But you're in the right area.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 伙计们 想在周五晚上去参加 托比 和\NHey, guys, you wanna come to a super fun party
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他朋友的有趣的聚会吗?\NOn Friday night with Toby and all his friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不去 - 是很正常的聚会\N- No way. - It's gonna be totally normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是\NNo, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 它的主题其实是长岛90年代的成人礼\NFine. it's long island '90s Bat Mitzvah theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,呃，嬉皮士\NUgh. Hipsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会觉得烦么?\NAren't you getting a little tired of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 总是那些衣服 古老的游戏\NI mean, the clothes, the antique yo-yos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你那个绳子已经弄了四个小时了\NYou've been making lanyards for four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去有好多事要做\NJust seems like a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么恋情是不需要努力的呢?\NWhat relationship isn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.98,0:13:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,阿弗莱克和加雷，他们的娃应该会想出来的\NAffleck and garner. Those kids got it figured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我承认\NOkay, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,认识什么是酷的  什么不酷真的很累人\NKnowing what's cool and what's not cool is exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但我正在学习 而且托比也值得我为他这么做\NBut I'm learning and Toby's worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,星期五来嘛就当为我?\NCome on Friday for me? There's gonna be
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,而且派对后还有个拇指摔跤锦标赛\NA thumb wrestling tournament at the after-party.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他们中有成年人吗?\NAre any of these people adults?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,成年礼之后他们就是了嘛\NThey will be after the bat mitzvah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,想想看吧 时间的起源遇上美食的未来\NImagine the beginning of time meets the future of food,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是 老兄...\NAnd that, my good man...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,泛大陆烧烤\NIs Pangaea grill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,同一个世界 同一个餐馆 --\NOne world. One restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:13:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,真是难以置信\NIncredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.68,0:14:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我得打电话叫我的合伙人过来\NI have to call my partners in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-棒极了 -等他们来了 你再演示一遍\N-Great. -And when they get here, pitch it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-没问题 -一模一样的\N-Okay. -Same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-没问题 -就假装你不知道\N-Okay. -As if you don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我听过的最傻逼的点子\NIt's the stupidest idea I've ever heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 你说什么?\NOkay. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我这回错大了\NI made a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.61,0:14:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-你不应该怪自己 -没 没 我没有\N-You can't blame yourself. -No, no, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的 我知道了 经济不景气\NYou know, I get it. Economy's bad, which is why
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我要绕开传统的找投资人这条路\NI'm gonna bypass the whole traditional investor thing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,自己出钱\NAnd cash in on my 401(k).
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.37,0:14:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,另外 和我一起干活的伙计告诉我\NPlus I'm working with this guy who told me a way
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以向他爸借点钱 听起来还行 对不?\NI can get a little cash from his dad. Sounds sketchy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,大错特错 我需要做的就是带一盒名片\NWrong. All I gotta do is take a box of calling cards
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,去印第安纳的飞机场\NTo an airfield in Indiana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,水到渠成\NCut and dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NAhem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦?\NWhat's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,想要淡啤酒?\NLight beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你们不相信我的烧烤王国计划?\NOkay, you don't--don't believe in this whole Pangaea thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.98,0:14:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我热爱餐馆\NI love restaurants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们--我们都喜欢...餐馆\NWe--we--we all love... Restaurants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我懂了 我懂了\NYeah, I get it. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫 别走嘛--嗯\NDave, come--ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 这件事的确很棘手\NWell, this is officially out of hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.36,0:15:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都不想跟他说点什么吗? 真的?\NAnd none of you guys is gonna say anything? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这是淡啤酒\NIt is light beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我来\NFine. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是因为\NAnd this all started as
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你们一开始说"谁能在僵尸大战中幸存下来"\NYour standard "Who would survive the zombie apocalypse?" debate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你们能想象如果我们真的\NCan you imagine what would happen
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,开始一场谈话会怎么样?\NIf we ever had a real conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂的 烧烤王国是个蠢毙了的点子\NI know. Pangaea was a stupid idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不啊...也不全是\NNo, not... Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就是...\NJust...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多很蠢的细节\NHad a lot of stupid stuff surrounding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫 我知道你觉得我是个"梦想粉碎机"\NDave, I know that you think that I'm a dream crusher,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这一次 我只想成为"梦想压缩机"\NBut in this case, I just wanna be a dream compactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这样...梦想\NLike... Dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 这不公平\NOkay, that's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你的手势让"压缩"都变得可爱了 那么..\NThe hand gestures make compacting look adorable, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这个庞大的计划不适合你 好吧?\NThis huge scheme is not you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你又理智又负责任\NYou're reasonable and responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:16:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 我又理智 又负责任\NI know. I'm so reasonable and I'm so responsible,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,都快把我变成个僵尸了\NIt turned me into a zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我心里非常明白\NAll right? I got that message loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 看嘛\NOkay, but look,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这有个折中的办法\NThere's a middle ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你没必要从零突然加速到六十码...\NYou don't need to go from zero to 60 in...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,随便吧 我不懂开车那玩意儿\NWhatever. I-I don't know car stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.71,0:16:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 你不需要寿司 你不需要哈萨克小吃\NLook, you don't need sushi. You don't need Kazak food.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你没必要取悦素食主义者\NYou don't need to try and make the Vegans happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他们永远不会开心的 做牛肉三明治 好吗?\NThey never will be. Steak sandwich, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,发挥你的特长 从小事做起\NStick with what you're good at. Start small.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,或许一间小小的三明治店铺\NA little sandwich shop, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,还是得贷点款\N-Still need to find some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你在向我求婚?\NAre you proposing to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我觉得我俩有段诡异的过去\N'cause I feel like we have a weird history.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你原来说过我可以留着它\NI know you said that I could keep it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在我想还给你，虽然不能完全的弥补一切\NBut I want you to have it. It's not gonna cover everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-这只是个开始 -谢谢你 阿莱\N-But it's a start. -Thanks, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 可以管我的店子叫"今夜牛排带回家"\NHey, I can call my shop "steak me home tonight."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:16:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-不 你不能这么叫 -好吧\N-No, you can't do that. -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你这么穿可不怎么残忍 简\NYou don't look very ruthless to me, Jane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,因为穿高跟鞋可跑不过僵尸\NCan't outrun a zombie in those heels.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.13,0:17:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,高中的时候 我穿高跟鞋打败过一个女生\NIn high school, I beat up a girl in these heels.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,诺艾尔就不该踩你\NNoelle should have never stepped to you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要是她想保留那一块头发的话\NIf she didn't wanna lose that hunk of hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-谢谢大伙捧场... -看我的卷发\N-You guys, thank you so much...  for coming! -Watch the crimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真不错 跟我来看九十年代的犹太成年礼吧\NYou look amazing. Let's get this '90s Bat Mitzvah on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,太疯狂了!\NIt's gonna be insanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.03,0:17:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.24,0:17:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 这没人盛装打扮啊\NUh, no one here's dressed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是超爱我的决定\NI am super happy with my choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 鱼丸~\NOoh, gefilte fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你们花了不少心思打扮吧\NYou guys seem to be putting in a lot of effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.02,0:17:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 为了这个90年代成年礼我们花了不少时间打扮\NYeah, we're just dressed for a '90s Bat Mitzvah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 卷发 犹太小帽 再明显不过了\NYeah, crimped hair, yarmulke. Seems a little obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.57,0:17:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,明显吗? 为化妆舞会打扮下不应该吗?\NObvious? To be dressing up for a costume party?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 这是个主题派对 是不一样的\NUm, this is a theme party. The's a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 打扮得太过了一点也不好\NLook, it's just not cool to try so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们太过了?\NWe are trying too hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,艾奥尼到哪都带着个空腰包\NIone wears an empty fanny pack everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.15,0:18:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,阿迪克斯每个周末都在二手市场\NAtticus spends his weekends at yard sales
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,到处找牛仔短裤\NScrounging around for jeans shorts,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他还叫阿迪克斯 我还看到你带耳麦了\NPlus his name is Atticus. I've seen you wearing headphones
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.79,0:18:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但是根本什么都没插\NThat aren't attached to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这个女孩子坐在个假轮椅上\NAnd this girl is in a fake wheelchair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.91,0:18:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的出了一场严重的车祸好吧\NI was in a really serious accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 老天 抱歉\NOh, my god. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,开玩笑的 我活蹦乱跳的 轮椅不错吧?\NJ.K. I can totes walk. Cool chair, th, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，老娘受够了\NOkay, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧你\NYou're done. Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 各位嬉皮士\Nlisten up, hipsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 也许我是打扮的太过了\Nyeah, maybe I do try too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题吧? 因为我们这么打扮会很有乐趣\NOkay? But that's because trying hard can be fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.43,0:18:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些人知道还有什么很有趣吗?\NAnd you know what else is fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.39,0:18:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真真正正喜欢点什么东西\NActually liking things,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.02,0:18:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就像这首歌 姐喜欢，非常喜欢\NLike this song. I like this song. I like it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.06,0:18:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不是讽刺你们 姐就喜欢\NNot ironically. I like it, like it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我的朋友也一样 伙计们 舞起来\NAnd so do my friends. Guys, we're dancing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.37,0:18:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.89,0:18:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这一点也不难为情\NThis is not awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:18:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 好了\NYou' done. Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,跳得好 注意脚下 晚安\NOkay. You're good. The legs. Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 小吃车 谢天谢地 姐要饿死了\NOh, a food truck. Thank god. I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-是啊 我也是的 -哦 饿死我了\N-Yeah, me, too. -Oh, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫?\NDavid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的吗? 太拉风了!\NIs this yours? It's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 我...听取了某人很好的一个建议\NI know. I... Got some really good advice
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,决定从小餐馆做起\NFrom a special person and decided to start small.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说我俩 兄弟\NIt's all about the brave-length, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不是说你 嗯 是阿莱克斯\NNo, no, not you. Uh, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我还不打算辞职\NSo I'm not gonna quit my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-这个餐车就是个兼职 -餐车现在很火\N-I'm just gonna do this part-time. -Food trucks are huge right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这个餐车真是太正点了 虽然不能开\NThis thing is awesome, although I cannot drive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,来的路上我肯定撞上什么东西了\NI definitely hit something on the way over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.83,0:19:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,撞了个人? 还是个木头? 或者是头猛兽?\NWas it a man? Was it a log? Was it a beast?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.87,0:19:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不得而知\NWe'll never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 兄弟们 是餐车也!\NHey, guys, food truck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 嬉皮士也喜欢小吃车\NHey, hipsters love food trucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄 我现在还没吃的\NDude, I don't have any food.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.97,0:19:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么? -哦 他们可不喜欢这样\N-What? -Ooh, they're not gonna like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不能失去我最大的客户群\NWell, I can't lose my biggest consumer base.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会在网上给我差评的\NThey'll tweet me out of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都上车 马科斯你去引开那些人\NEverybody get in the truck. Max, you distract the hipsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.45,0:19:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 帅哥! 看那边!\NHey, everybody! Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.45,0:19:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,索菲亚 科波拉在那边打羽毛球\NSofia Coppola's playing badminton
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.02,0:20:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,跟杰森 施沃茨曼 一起!\NWith Jason Schwartzman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,开车! 开车!\NDrive! Drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚在那些嬉皮士面前表现不错嘛\NImpressive moves back there with those hipsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,或许我们都能打赢僵尸大战\NMaybe we'd both do oka in a zombie apocalypse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,开玩笑? 只要我们联合起来\NAre you kidding? With our skills combined,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们就能战无不胜 -哦 一大波僵尸来了\N-We'd be unstoppable. -Oh, there's more of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,什么? 哦!\NWhat? Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,冷酷无情! 哇!\NRuthlessness! Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 真够哥们\Nall right, okay. Very funny, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,把你们的朋友扔到路边 开慢点\NThrow your friend out of a car. Slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫 开慢点 我不能跑步 人家还没热身\NDave, slow down. I can't run. I didn't stretch today,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,别--停下来 完了 腿抽筋了 戴夫\NSo don't--slow down. All right, pulled my hamstring, Dave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫 人家腿抽筋了! 慢点!\NDave, I pulled my hammy out! Slow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,另一条腿也抽筋了! 另一条腿也抽筋了!\NI pulled my other hamstring out! I pulled my other hamstring out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫! 戴夫 你是--\NDave! Dave, you're--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,太不够朋友了!\NThis is not something that friends do to each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,人家腿抽筋了!\NI have a cramp!

